{"tid":2445140,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透討論] 點睇講暗殺金囝紀錄片《金氏殺機》(Assassins)","createTime":"2021-03-13T11:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T18:55:23.000Z","uid":4260,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a178a022fcd6fd764838179844b94e05bedf3ce7","tid":2445140,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.wmoov.com/movie/photo/202012/FB_IMG_1607278297726_1607520483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.wmoov.com%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F202012%2FFB_IMG_1607278297726_1607520483.jpg&h=523f367c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PJDj-NAA8a0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPJDj-NAA8a0&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=5f6b7c4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PJDj-NAA8a0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好精彩、光怪陸離，好撚癡線嘅紀錄片<br />\n話係一套現實嘅政治驚悚片唔過份，成件事實在太juicy<br />\n<br />\n一宗暗殺案背後帶出非常多議題：國際政治、販賣人口、法治(外國)都係死的<br />\n當中嘅政治陰謀講得唔算太深入<br />\n但探討兩個女人嘅背景同事態發展足夠曲折離奇<br />\n<br />\n去一次東京迪士尼足以觸發權力鬥爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿論結果如何，後續嘅傷害係一世的<br />\n睇完有少少擔心紀錄片制作組安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發覺少人講，推介一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567ccb7bf579fc7b68daabb38718bc5efef56441","tid":2445140,"uid":59818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老味入場之前都估唔到最尾會睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a4b2c90349ce99819638101a84d629ecde7bc3","tid":2445140,"uid":4260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"567ccb7bf579fc7b68daabb38718bc5efef56441","tid":2445140,"uid":59818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTi